    <item>
      <title>爱荷华州警长和前奥运选手在赛跑中被五年级学生击败</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/18/1252245744/iowa-superintendent-and-former-olympian-bested-in-footrace-by-5th-grader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊恩·罗伯茨参加过一些世界上最引人注目的比赛。但迄今为止，他最大的竞争对手是一位穿着牛仔短裤和耐克网球鞋、意志坚定的五年级学生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/18/1252245744/iowa-superintendent-and-former-olympian-bested-in-footrace-by-5th-grader</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 09:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
